I decided to make my journal FRIENDS ONLY. This is nothing personal or anything, it was just something that had to be done. If you want to be added: -comment Some things you must know: -I love my cat. I take random pictures of her. -I take random pictures of anything. -I work at Questar Gas. I have Questar drama. I talk about it. -I don't have a boy but I have many I enjoy. I ask for advice on those boys. -I typo. -I post after drinking and usually tell people to call me. -I love comments. -I love the following and if you don't, you probably don't want to read: Brand New, The Golden Girls, Roswell, that one bass player, Saved By The Bell. If you have a problem with any of the above....you don't want to be here. Also...if you want to add me, please comment here. Don't just add me and never comment. I don't mind you adding me first, but when I go to my info page and see that three people added me and didn't comment, it pisses me off. It's common courtesy. Just let me know. I'm nice, I wont hurt you...unless...you don't comment. I write a lot, and it's weird, obscure, and sometimes comes out making no sense at all. I really, really, REALLY like feedback, good or bad, so if you feel so inclinded, please read and enjoy. I really am a nice person. But...you break-a my rules...I break-a your face. Deal? Peace~Jordan
